Job Description:
- Oversee and manage yearly performance appraisal that drives high performance;
- Conduct employee orientation and training programs;
- Provide consultation to the manager related to employee relations issues, and managing all disciplinary issues within the company;
- Maintain historical human resource and company records by designing a filing and retrieval system; keeping past and current records;
